Text:
I love your uploads. Thank you for your efforts.  Is there any chance you can get your hands on the IDW Wire Hangers series only issues 1 & 2 are floating around the rest are MIA. Your upload of this would be appreciated.

Thanks again for all of your great work.
I can upload 01 and 02,but the rest aren`t out yet...

Thanks for your quick response.  When you say that they are not out, you mean they have not been submitted by anyone? Pardon my ignorance on this as I am new.  They wrapped up 1-4 already and also introduced the graphic novel tying the series back in Nov 10, 2010. It just seems that all the reliable up-loaders stopped at issue 2.  Thanks again, you are truly appreciated.
scanovic:yep I know about the graphic novel,but nobody scanned it,so until that happens I can't upload it...

I lol when it says on the cover "Still ONLY 399 cents!"
I really wish they would just stay at $2.99 :(
